t: Teuma meunyo ka jih laen ulah Í Meunyo jipaleng han jimeuiman Takheun wateenyan sep lon ngon Allah Tan Tuhan laen nibak Droeneuhnyan Tawakai keunan di lon meunyerah Ka lon peujok droe di lon bak Tuhan d Cit Droeneuh Tuhan Po milek ‘arasy ‘Arasy nyang raya han ek tatuban Makheuluk Tuhan raya sileupah